data.description: Ever wondered what it's like to have your own forest retreat and private backyard greeted by nature's symphony? Spread over a captivating acre, nestled at the end of a secluded cul-de-sac, this gem awaits your discovery! Step inside a generously spacious well-maintained home with ample storage and flex space. Gleaming brand-new stainless-steel appliances, nice countertops, backsplash, white cabinets, eating area, and pantry in the kitchen on a hardwood floor. New carpet in the owner’s suite, two secondary bedrooms, family room, and hallway upstairs. Freshly painted interior, back deck, and recently pressured-washed exterior. Nice-sized laundry room too! Sizable 2-car garage with a workshop! Newer HVAC system (only two-years old). New gutter guard system, and roof inspected every year with no issues. Long driveway (recently pressured washed) with plenty of parking space. Sellers have maintained termite bond and service, and existing Home Warranty is transferable to buyers. No HOA! Conveniently located minutes from downtown Statham, Athens, and Winder. Sellers downsizing. This could be the sanctuary you've been searching for! Schedule your showing today!
